products.description2: The iPhone 14 Pro Max display has rounded corners that follow a beautiful curved design, and these corners are within a standard rectangle. When measured as a standard rectangular shape, the screen is 6.69 inches diagonally (actual viewable area is less). Both models: Dynamic Island. The iPhone 14 Pro and 14 Pro Max have now launched the action mode, designed to capture clear, high-quality videos with just one hand – even when the person recording is moving around. The phone debuts a new processor – the A16 Bionic – and offers four potential storage options: 128 GB, 256 GB, 512 GB and 1TB.

products.title: One Plus
products.description2: Smartphones. OnePlus releases two lines of smartphones: its flagship "OnePlus" line, and its budget-oriented Nord line. Both lines are equipped with an Android-based operating system known as OxygenOS. OnePlus has also released phones outside of these lines, namely the OnePlus Ace and the OnePlus 10R.
